Una was an 8-year-old who dreamed of UFOs. One night, she heard a strange noise outside her window and saw a UFO hovering above her house. She quickly ran outside to get a closer look. Una was amazed by the sight and wanted to understand what it was doing there. She followed the UFO until it stopped at the nearby park. Una used her curiosity to uncover the truth and found out that the UFO was actually a group of kids playing a game of hide-and-seek!
